# 👨‍💼 Employee Management Portal

A full-stack web application built using **Spring Boot**, **React**, and **MySQL** to efficiently manage employee records. The application allows users to perform complete CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations through a modern web interface and RESTful APIs.

---

## 🚀 Features

* ➕ Add new employees
* 📋 View all employee records
* ✏️ Update employee information
* 🗑️ Delete employees
* 🔄 REST API integration between frontend and backend
* 💾 MySQL database connectivity
* 📱 Responsive and user-friendly interface

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

### Backend

* Java 17
* Spring Boot
* Spring Data JPA
* Hibernate
* REST APIs
* Gradle

### Frontend

* React.js
* JavaScript (ES6+)
* HTML5
* CSS3
* Axios

### Database

* MySQL

### Tools

* Git & GitHub
* IntelliJ IDEA
* VS Code
* Postman

