## ⚙️ Getting Started

### Prerequisites

* Java 17+
* Node.js
* MySQL Server
* Git

---

### Backend Setup

```bash
cd Backend
gradlew bootRun
```

Configure your database credentials in:

```properties
src/main/resources/application.properties
```

---

### Frontend Setup

```bash
cd Frontend
npm install
npm start
```

Frontend runs at:

```text
http://localhost:3000
```

Backend runs at:

```text
http://localhost:8080
```

